(13, 1, '2013-11-12 19:53:29', '2013-11-12 19:53:29', '<h2>POWERSCHOOL PARENT PORTAL</h2>\r\nParents/guardians and students are encouraged to visit PowerSchool on a regular basis to get immediate access to student grades, attendance records, course outlines and more.\r\n\r\n<img class="alignright" alt="" src="http://gvc.gvsd.ca/images/images/powerschool/powerschool_logo.jpg" width="658" height="167" />\r\n\r\nAccess the Parent Portal ONLINE BY CLICKING HERE.\r\n\r\nAccess the Parent Portal on Your Mobile Device\r\n\r\nClick here for step-by-step instructions.\r\n\r\nAccess the Student Portal on Your Mobile Device\r\nClick here for step-by-step instructions.\r\n\r\nIf you would like information about setting up your PowerSchool Parent account, adding your children, and resetting your password please choose from the documnets below.\r\n\r\nHow to Create a Parent Access Account\r\nThis document will guide you through the process of setting up an account\r\n\r\nAdding Students to Accounts\r\nThis document will explain how to add students to your account\r\n\r\nHow to Recover Passwords\r\nThis document will show you how to recover a password if you have forgotten it\r\n\r\nParent Portal User Guide\r\nThis document is an overview of the entire parent portal\r\n\r\nFor additional help, contact Susana Hawryshko at (204) 325-8008.', 'Parents', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'parents', '', '', '2013-12-05 19:20:55', '2013-12-05 19:20:55', '', 0, 'http://gvc.preview.clc.tf/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
